{"tid":1781602,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"(發洩post)有冇人覺得自己好燈, 係天生嘅燈神","createTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-14T10:25:07.000Z","uid":254330,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"30d096a4a73a8bbf2a28f6daa65b4eb53c73d3d7","tid":1781602,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:35:42.000Z","msg":"燈, 一個字就足夠形容我成個人, 無論邊方面都會比我燈死<br />\n有時係唔好嘅, 但係有時都會帶黎 benefits<br />\n不過真係搞到自己完全唔想有幻想, 講野之前都要諗諗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n講感情, 以為自己都叫對對方好好, 點知佢根本唔撚受, 當係老奉咁;以為自己都叫合格嘅companion, 原來係對方眼中根本唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n講運氣, 有去開日本睇各種live, 去自己真心想去嘅concert之前都會FF自己有得坐神席, 點知每次都係抽中山頂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 有時仲冇飛; 去陪frd睇or 純粹冇野做路過入場睇嘅concert就次鳩次都勁撚前 唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> (btw 不支持炒飛<br />\n<br />\n幫人, 好多時幫完人做野之後都會FF下, expect當自己有事嘅時候佢會幫番你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 結果大多都係覆sor 唔得閒 (雖然我都明有班frd係真係好忙嘅) , 另外自己幫人之後總係會後悔, 屌 早知唔撚幫佢<br />\n係個人際遇問題定真係太燈?<br />\n<br />\n之前諗住我地可以透過機場贏, 渣實政府春袋, 所以我自己都係和你飛嘅前1日就入機場接機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 係果晚裏面識左幾個都係打算透過機場贏嘅巴絲, 傾過下之後點做,點知第日就bye bye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />, 出禁制令,自己仲同果班巴絲FF左好多野, 依家懷疑本身work都比我燈死左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買股票, 尋日先諗住今日做熊軍, 講完唔夠1個鐘, 侵侵就出tweet, 然後夜期升到仆街,到930本身mark低左想入嘅熊已經死左。自己又鍾意set低幾個價位入貨, 點知佢唔撚跌, 係咁升, 買唔到走曬寶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 例如今日隻9966咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有 ipo中簽率奇低, 阿里巴巴都抽唔撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />(利申冇玩孖展) 不過都好彩, 侵侵尋晚就講消息, 如果唔係今日應該入熊 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n有時趕時間嘅時候, 個心越急就越多意外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  搭的士沿途都會有其他車係d大路炒車塞死曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n之前試過約frd出黎, 冇野做, 果晚星期三,佢話不如去馬會賭馬, 我心諗我乜鳩都唔識, 未接觸過, 但係佢死都要去玩。咁我話贏左就留輸左就走la, 結果只係跟tg grp嘅tips, 贏撚到最尾果場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 雖然我到依家都係唔撚識點買, 但係發現入場講得呢句就多數有錢收<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2128b2027b94883e4d8be156314b5146854d636b","tid":1781602,"uid":254330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:37:06.000Z","msg":"諗野之前真係唔敢諗正面<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n怕燈死自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n燒山都係燈我地姐, 我成鳩日燈自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82547a72463b40efbcb93de930a795f2437b75fb","tid":1781602,"uid":254330,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:40:36.000Z","msg":"順便當宣傳下呢個helmat, 推比家長睇<br />\n<br />\n日本可摺疊式頭盔「折り畳みヘルメット」用家報告<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1768846\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1768846</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n諗住派膠咁話驚香港有地震,叫大家買頭盔, 點知長洲即刻有地震 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58b05548a6b9796af1944ab8a0582229c84bc92f","tid":1781602,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-13T09:41:47